HEADWORD: Balsamical
<hw>Bal*sam"ic*al</hw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>balsamique</ets>.]</ety> <def>Having the qualities of balsam;
containing, or resembling, balsam; soft; mitigative; soothing;
restorative.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

